basics.label: Test Analyst-Intern/Contractor
basics.summary: 3+ years of professional experience in Software Testing with a strong passion for delivering quality software. Strong analytical and problem solving skills with expertise in Manual and Automation testing of various web and mobile-based applications. Worked in E-commerce, Banking and Insurance domains. Proven ability to multi-task and prioritize effectively with excellent Risk Management skills and ability to meet tight deadlines. ISTQB certified tester.
